can destroy the world.

833
01:30:07,593 --> 01:30:10,255
There are not just 400 tonnes
in the world.

834
01:30:11,597 --> 01:30:13,588
You can lie without responsibilities.

835
01:30:13,833 --> 01:30:15,824
You won't think about it.

836
01:30:16,570 --> 01:30:22,236
Dad is worried about our safety.

837
