Please let me calm down.

842
01:31:49,662 --> 01:31:53,996
Hydrogen bomb explosion?
How great is that.

843
01:31:57,904 --> 01:32:00,896
Too worried, stupid.

844
01:32:01,273 --> 01:32:03,104
Just let the minister worry.

845
01:32:03,742 --> 01:32:09,078
Only to drop the earth
to avoid radiation.

846
01:32:57,631 --> 01:33:01,795
To dad this result is not bad.

847
01:33:50,450 --> 01:33:53,442
ls it Mr. Yuen? Thanks for your help.

848
01:33:54,354 --> 01:33:58,256
No worries.

849
01:33:59,426 --> 01:34:01,087
Coming to visit dad?

850
01:34:02,129 --> 01:34:07,294
l can leave him.

851
01:34:09,436 --> 01:34:14,100
l think the judgment was wrong.

852
01:34:15,009 --> 01:34:20,345
lt's our fault.

853
01:34:22,181 --> 01:34:26,845
Should bring this to the court.

854
01:34:26,987 --> 01:34:28,545
Should have sent dad here early.

855
01:34:30,756 --> 01:34:35,250
To all of us it's a good result.

856
01:34:37,965 --> 01:34:39,956
You go to see dad.

857
01:34:50,410 --> 01:34:52,071
Excuse me.

858
01:35:26,346 --> 01:35:34,014
l am down to see the patient.

859
01:35:37,323 --> 01:35:38,984
lt's the first time to come across.

860
01:35:40,995 --> 01:35:46,831
Every mad man is the same.

861
01:35:49,970 --> 01:35:54,964
But when seeing the patient.

862
01:35:59,479 --> 01:36:03,142
The feeling is different.

863
01:36:03,449 --> 01:36:09,945
He makes me feel uncomfortable.

864
01:36:13,762 --> 01:36:17,095
Anyway he's mad.

865
01:36:20,534 --> 01:36:27,702
Or we are really the mad man.

866
01:36:38,686 --> 01:36:40,017
Please come over.

867
01:37:48,888 --> 01:37:50,549
l am Yuen.

868
01:38:00,635 --> 01:38:04,298
Thanks for coming.

869
01:38:06,274 --> 01:38:10,768
Welcome.

870
01:38:14,114 --> 01:38:20,610
lt's safe to stay here, no worries.

871
01:38:25,727 --> 01:38:32,223
How about the earth now?

872
01:38:34,702 --> 01:38:37,034
Human is living?

873
01:38:40,574 --> 01:38:42,735
Life is going on?

874
01:38:47,648 --> 01:38:52,142
lt's not possible.

875
01:38:53,388 --> 01:38:56,380
Regrets if you don't escape.

876
01:38:58,025 --> 01:39:00,016
Why don't they understand?

877
01:39:02,263 --> 01:39:06,097
Must leave this planet ASAP.

878
01:39:07,335 --> 01:39:09,166
Hurry to this planet.

879
01:39:11,306 --> 01:39:14,139
ls it burning?

880
01:39:18,680 --> 01:39:21,012
